These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
Color: yellow, grey, lilac
1. Color:grey is on the right of Color:lilac##1
2. Color:yellow is on the far right##1
3. Color:yellow is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Color   | lilac | grey | yellow |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
Hobby: reading, writing, chess
1. Hobby:writing is in an odd position##4
2. Hobby:reading is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Hobby   | reading | chess | writing |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
Movie-Genre: action, western, family
1. Movie-Genre:western is in an even position##4
2. Movie-Genre:western is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:family##3
3. Movie-Genre:family is on the right of Movie-Genre:western##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Movie-Genre   | action | western | family |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-4::.
Job: police-officer, fisherman, entrepreneur
1. Job:fisherman is in an odd position##4
2. Job:entrepreneur is on the left of Job:fisherman##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |  3   |
| Job   | police-officer | entrepreneur | fisherman |

