.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-8::.
Music-Genre: electronic, house, classical
1. Music-Genre:classical is in an odd position##4
2. Music-Genre:house == Music-Genre:house##1
3. Music-Genre:classical is on the right of Music-Genre:house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |     2     |    3    |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | house | classical |

